247
00:21:50,930 --> 00:21:56,470
Ah, Sunbae. For something like this, you're supposed to file a report

248
00:21:56,470 --> 00:22:00,310
and get a warrant before the police can search for him.

249
00:22:00,960 --> 00:22:03,340
