266
00:23:47,190 --> 00:23:49,690
 Wait a minute. Wait a minute. 

267
00:23:49,690 --> 00:23:53,070
Stay right there, be careful. Be careful.

268
00:23:53,080 --> 00:23:54,430
Go.

269
00:23:54,430 --> 00:23:56,140
Where's your lawn mower?

270
00:23:56,140 --> 00:23:57,560
My lawn mower?

271
00:23:57,560 --> 00:23:59,000
