274
00:24:03,020 --> 00:24:07,490
I won't ask for money. Is that a shed? It must be in there.

275
00:24:07,490 --> 00:24:09,710
I told you not to do work!

276
00:24:12,290 --> 00:24:16,190
I'll feed you as I promised. Sleep over there tonight.

277
00:24:16,190 --> 00:24:17,770
Leave here tomorrow.

278
00:24:27,860 --> 00:24:30,470
It's not opening yet.

279
00:24:30,470 --> 00:24:34,890
Just wait a bit. They'll definitely open it for us.

280
00:24:36,160 --> 00:24:37,570
 Connecting... 

281
00:24:37,570 --> 00:24:41,280
We're getting a signal.

282
00:24:43,020 --> 00:24:45,160
What are you all doing?

283
00:24:45,160 --> 00:24:47,810
Everyone, start searching.

284
00:24:47,810 --> 00:24:49,720
Yes!

285
00:25:05,070 --> 00:25:07,230
Excuse me.

286
00:25:08,710 --> 00:25:10,870
Your companion probably needs to eat too.

287
00:25:10,870 --> 00:25:12,650
She told me not to wake her until we land.

288
00:25:12,650 --> 00:25:14,150
Ah, I see.

289
00:25:14,150 --> 00:25:16,740
She drank too much yesterday.

290
00:25:16,740 --> 00:25:20,260
I understand. Enjoy your meal.

291
00:26:03,300 --> 00:26:07,650
