♬   And be careful of the wolf  ♬

295
00:26:24,500 --> 00:26:26,890
 Where's my father? 

296
00:26:28,360 --> 00:26:30,540
 Drink this. It's motion sickness medicine. 

297
00:26:30,540 --> 00:26:32,960
 Where's my father? 

298
00:26:32,960 --> 00:26:35,000
 If you drink this, your father will come. 

299
00:26:35,000 --> 00:26:36,950
 That's a lie. 

300
00:26:38,040 --> 00:26:43,630
 Yeah, it's a lie. Your father is not coming anymore. 

301
00:26:43,630 --> 00:26:47,280
 I want to go to my father. Take me to my father. 

302
00:26:49,800 --> 00:26:54,470
♬   Be good in the meantime  ♬

303
00:26:54,470 --> 00:27:00,140
♬   Keep the door locked  ♬

304
00:27:00,140 --> 00:27:08,270
♬   And be careful of the wolf  ♬

305
00:27:39,680 --> 00:27:44,320
I'm sorry. This is all we have to eat.

306
00:27:44,320 --> 00:27:47,280
We only eat to live.

307
00:27:47,990 --> 00:27:49,880
It's okay.

308
00:27:56,220 --> 00:28:00,570
I'm sorry for getting angry earlier.

309
00:28:17,630 --> 00:28:18,840
I found him!

310
00:28:18,840 --> 00:28:22,280
What? Where is he?

311
00:28:22,280 --> 00:28:23,920
He's here.

312
00:28:23,920 --> 00:28:26,010
- When was this? 
 - This morning.

313
00:28:26,010 --> 00:28:30,070
However, he disappeared after he entered the bathroom.

314
00:28:30,070 --> 00:28:32,390
He must have changed his clothes.

315
00:28:32,390 --> 00:28:35,590
Track everyone who leaves from here.

316
00:28:35,590 --> 00:28:37,550
Yes.

317
00:28:40,890 --> 00:28:46,430
Yes, you punk.  Please help me to save my face (reputation).

318
00:29:29,830 --> 00:29:30,920
 Why? 

319
00:29:30,920 --> 00:29:34,540
 It's a minefield. Everyone, get out. 

320
00:29:38,230 --> 00:29:40,410
 What? I can't walk. 

321
00:29:40,410 --> 00:29:45,050
 Hey, listen to him. He saved my life. 

322
00:29:56,000 --> 00:30:00,900
 Hey, we're entering a civilian territory. We have to take a detour. 

323
00:30:00,900 --> 00:30:04,650
