 - I'm going to pay you double the amount you get paid here. 

328
00:30:15,080 --> 00:30:16,760
 Just go. 

329
00:30:16,760 --> 00:30:20,170
 - No. 
 - Three times. 

330
00:30:20,170 --> 00:30:22,020
 Back off. 

331
00:30:22,020 --> 00:30:24,050
 What about you? 

332
00:30:41,620 --> 00:30:45,380
 Hey! Go! Get out of here! 

333
00:30:57,850 --> 00:31:00,020
 Go now! 

334
00:32:32,450 --> 00:32:35,060
Want a sip?

335
00:32:44,660 --> 00:32:48,730
Today is the 49th day after our son's death.  (Koreans believe one's spirit will be appointed to the special places on the 49th day after one's death.) 

336
00:32:48,730 --> 00:32:51,750
We were on our way back from the temple earlier.  (Some people pray for the deceased on the 49th day after one's death.) 

337
00:33:10,490 --> 00:33:16,830
Fruit trees are just like children. Since the caregiver was gone,

338
00:33:16,830 --> 00:33:19,060
trees immediately turned into this mess.

339
00:33:19,060 --> 00:33:21,590
Now I will just close down this orchard.

340
00:33:21,590 --> 00:33:23,320
Since no one wants to buy it from me,

341
00:33:23,320 --> 00:33:27,830
I'm going to cut all the trees down and burn them.

342
00:33:49,680 --> 00:33:51,760
Mister,

343
00:33:51,760 --> 00:33:55,580
could you cut all of these down for me?

344
00:33:59,320 --> 00:34:00,340
Are you serious?

345
00:34:00,340 --> 00:34:03,910
Yes. Cut them all down.

346
00:34:03,910 --> 00:34:08,950
It's hard for me to do it by myself.

347
00:34:12,860 --> 00:34:14,790
Okay.

348
00:34:15,770 --> 00:34:20,860
Yeah? My heart feels lighter.

349
00:34:20,860 --> 00:34:27,880
Then, please do it tomorrow. I'll give you cash in return.

350
00:34:30,560 --> 00:34:35,490
I feel better. My heart feels relieved.

351
00:34:48,470 --> 00:34:52,740
Let's all hang in there. Fighting.

352
00:34:52,740 --> 00:34:55,510
Good, good. We must catch him for sure.

353
00:34:55,510 --> 00:34:57,330
How are you going to catch him being this tired?

354
00:34:57,330 --> 00:35:02,280
Let's keep our eyes wide open and catch him.

355
00:35:32,810 --> 00:35:39,000
Yes, cut them all down.

356
00:36:58,660 --> 00:37:01,660
President.  President.

357
00:37:02,490 --> 00:37:04,270
We found him.

358
00:37:04,970 --> 00:37:08,570
What? You found him?

359
00:37:30,020 --> 00:37:34,130
You can stay here longer if you want.

360
00:37:36,020 --> 00:37:39,910
If you insist on having me, I can stay a bit longer.

361
00:37:46,270 --> 00:37:49,140
This is delicious.

362
00:37:52,140 --> 00:37:55,220
This belonged to my deceased son.

363
00:37:55,220 --> 00:38:00,740
If that doesn't bother you, you can wear it while you work.

364
00:38:06,640 --> 00:38:09,140
It looks like it will fit me just right.

365
00:38:11,030 --> 00:38:12,760
Thank you.

366
00:38:32,300 --> 00:38:36,140
Grandpa, do you have any more weedwacker blades?

367
00:38:36,140 --> 00:38:37,210
I don't think so.

368
00:38:37,210 --> 00:38:39,210
Then, I'll go buy some more.

369
00:39:21,140 --> 00:39:22,800
Is she feeling ill?

370
00:39:22,800 --> 00:39:26,780
No, she just drank too much yesterday.

371
00:39:26,780 --> 00:39:29,100
Please let me know if you need any help.

372
00:40:11,080 --> 00:40:14,250
No. No.  What are you doing?

373
00:40:18,910 --> 00:40:22,950
I'll ask you one more time.

374
00:40:27,100 --> 00:40:28,800
Where is this guy?

375
00:40:28,800 --> 00:40:33,080
I don't know. He left this morning.

376
00:40:36,910 --> 00:40:41,160
I understand. If you don't know, I have no other choice.

377
00:40:44,670 --> 00:40:47,500
W-W-What are you doing?

378
00:40:47,500 --> 00:40:49,680
No, no! No!

379
00:40:49,680 --> 00:40:52,730
Don't do that! Don't do that!

380
00:40:54,460 --> 00:40:56,660
Don't. Don't.

381
00:40:56,660 --> 00:40:59,240
Don't do that.

382
00:41:00,740 --> 00:41:02,390
Don't.

383
00:41:02,390 --> 00:41:06,180
Don't!

384
00:41:06,180 --> 00:41:08,330
No!

